{"lemma":"غِرَّةٌ","slug":"غِرَّةٌ","root":"غ.ر.ر","root_slug":"غ-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31588"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"white spot, blaze"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the prime, the cutting edge, remoteness from the bad"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"beginning, onset, outset"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inadvertency, lack of particular attention or equipment"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣur.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31588","headword_ar":"غِرَّةٌ","root":"gr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Negligence; inattention; inadvertence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inadvertency; inconsiderateness; heedlessness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unpreparedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gir~aAtN","text_ar":"غِرَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girarN","text_ar":"غِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see an ex. of the former in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaEa","text_ar":"شَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and exs. of both in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraY","text_ar":"دَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algir~apu tajolibu Ald~ir~apa","text_ar":"الغِرَّةُ تَجْلِبُ الدِّرَّةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inadvertence brings the means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paucity of milk causes to come abundance thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to him who gives little and from whom much is hoped for afterwards. (Meyd. [See Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 179: and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girAarN","text_ar":"غِراَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY gir~apK","text_ar":"عَلَى غِرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"On an occasion of negligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unexpectedly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErD","text_ar":"عرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano gir~apK","text_ar":"عَنْ غِرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In consequence of inadvertence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zalaqN","text_ar":"زَلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inexperience in affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gir~apN","text_ar":"غِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaArapN","text_ar":"غَرَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same. (A'Obeyd.) [The latter is an inf. n.: see 1.] See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gur~apN","text_ar":"غُرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", second sentence. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gir~apN biA@ll~`hi","text_ar":"غِرَّةٌ بِا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Boldness against God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)       -A2-  [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gir~N","text_ar":"غِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"غرة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23444#ef9c9f","body_html":"<span>الغرة: من العبيد هو الذي يكون ثمنه نصف عشر الدية. </span>"}]}}